snippet.title: Jerry's Merry Christmas Walkthrough - Merry Christmas !!
snippet.description:
Play "Jerry's Merry Christmas" game at their sponsor MouseCity.com:
http://www.mousecity.com/games/point-and-click/jerrys-merry-christmas/

Ho, ho ho! Jerry is one day late for doing his Christmas preparations. He did most of the decorating, but only the recognizable Xmas Mistletoe is missing! You must help him to save Xmas!
You are currently watching "Jerry's Merry Christmas Walkthrough" video, which was recorded and completed in less than 3 mins.
